claim.claim-text:
1. A novelty device comprising: 
a) a housing having an outside region and an inside region; 
b) a cover attached to said outside region of said housing; 
c) an energy source disposed within said housing; 
d) a noise maker disposed within said housing and connected to said energy source; and 
e) a timer connected to said noise maker and said energy source wherein said timer is designed to signal said noise maker to make a noise after a period of time.
